text: Mount Yushi () is a mountain in Dongyang township, Guangfeng District of Shangrao, Jiangxi, China. It is the highest mountain in the northeastern Guangfeng District. It belongs to Danxia landform. On the top of the mountain, there is a Buddhist temple named "Yushi Temple" (). ==References== Category:Tourist attractions in Shangrao Category:Geography of Shangrao Yushi
title: Mount Yushi
